summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 9321 entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of 5th Avenue South, in the City of Seattle, from Yesler Way to Jackson Street, by replanking the same, all in accordance with Resolution No. 512; and providing for the payment therefor by mode of 'Immediate Payment' under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
